#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#   AI4REALNET D1.3 BlueSky scenario for testing the RL models on realistic data
#   Env: CentralisedStaticObstacleSectorCREnv-v0
#   Authors: Giulia Leto
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Start sim at full speed
#00:00:00.00>OP
#00:00:00.00>DTMULT 5000

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#   Pan and zoom in on area, disable visible waypoints and airports
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
00:00:00.00>PAN 45.5 0
00:00:00.00>ZOOM 0.03

00:00:00.00> showapt 0
00:00:00.00> showwpt 0
00:00:00.00> LABEL 0

00:00:00.00>TRAIL ON
00:00:00.00>TAXI OFF 1000

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#   Creates polygons for the Lisbon FIR
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
00:00:00.00> PCALL ai4realnet_deploy_RL/sector.scn

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#   Creates polygons for the restricted areas
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
00:00:00.00> PCALL ai4realnet_deploy_RL/CentralisedStaticObstacleSectorCREnv-v0/restricted_areas-sample.scn

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#   Load aircraft origin and destinations
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
00:00:00.00> PCALL ai4realnet_deploy_RL/CentralisedStaticObstacleSectorCREnv-v0/flights-sample.scn

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#   Load the "DEPLOY_RL_CentralisedStaticObstacleSectorCREnv" plugin
#   - select which model to run
#   - reads the simulation state 
#   - trained RL model issues speed/heading changes to aircraft
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
00:00:00.00>PLUGIN DEPLOY_RL_CentralisedStaticObstacleSectorCREnv